## Remarks
 <span data-ttu-id="e4811-103"><xref:System.Web.Configuration.AuthorizationSection> クラスを使用すると、構成ファイルの `authorization` セクションにプログラムからアクセスして変更できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e4811-103">The <xref:System.Web.Configuration.AuthorizationSection> class provides a way to programmatically access and modify the `authorization` section of a configuration file.</span></span>

 <span data-ttu-id="e4811-104">この型は、<xref:System.Web.Configuration.AuthorizationRule>、<xref:System.Web.Configuration.AuthorizationRuleCollection>、および <xref:System.Web.Configuration.AuthorizationRuleAction> の種類を含むグループの一部です。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e4811-104">This type is part of a group that includes the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.AuthorizationRule>, the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.AuthorizationRuleCollection>, and the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.AuthorizationRuleAction> types.</span></span>

> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="e4811-105"><xref:System.Web.Configuration.AuthorizationSection> は、値が <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationAllowDefinition.Everywhere>のセクションプロパティ <xref:System.Configuration.SectionInformation.AllowDefinition%2A> に従って、構成ファイルの関連セクションに対して情報の読み取りと書き込みを行うことができます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e4811-105">The <xref:System.Web.Configuration.AuthorizationSection> can read and write information from and to the related section of the configuration file according to the section property <xref:System.Configuration.SectionInformation.AllowDefinition%2A> whose value is <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationAllowDefinition.Everywhere>.</span></span>



